{"tid":17621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香港勁揪】再創歷史　「牛丸」陳婉婷封亞洲最佳女教練","createTime":"2016-12-02T01:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T03:03:44.000Z","uid":35221,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb8581bf69aa635ddd7318db9a6d4bcd3d55a532","tid":17621,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:50:33.000Z","msg":"【香港勁揪】再創歷史　牛丸封亞洲最佳女教練 (17:34)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20161202/s00006/1480613477636SL4_819F0FF47DEF1FA077C73F41513A3863.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20161202%2Fs00006%2F1480613477636SL4_819F0FF47DEF1FA077C73F41513A3863.jpg&h=28ca34b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n28歲的東方龍獅主帥陳婉婷（牛丸）再次揚威海外，昨晚於亞洲足協（AFC）頒獎禮當選「年度最佳女教練」。今年屢獲殊榮的牛丸以「奇妙」形容成為男子職業球隊的女主帥，並感激東方給予的機會和信任。<br />\n<br />\n牛丸昨遠赴阿布扎比競逐亞洲足協「年度最佳女教練」，正裝出席的她力壓日本女子U17國家隊教練岡本三代及朝鮮的李恩淑獲此亞洲足壇最高殊榮，牛丸獲獎後將榮譽歸於球隊：「能在一隊男子職業隊成為教練十分奇妙，因此我要感謝東方給我的機會和信任，以及所有職球員。」<br />\n<br />\n前月才滿28歲的牛丸度過豐收一年，去年12月走馬上任帶領東方贏得銀牌冠軍及聯賽錦標後，個人榮譽亦接踵而來。5月先獲健力士世界紀錄認可為「全球首位率領男子職業足球隊問鼎頂級聯賽冠軍的女教練」及當選香港足球明星選舉「最佳教練」，7月再獲特區政府頒授銅紫荊星章，上月更入選英國廣播公司（BBC）「年度百大女性」，為香港體壇首人。<br />\n<br />\n另外，效力艾阿恩的阿聯酋中場鴨都拉曼（Omar Abdulrahman）雖剛在亞冠決賽屈居亞軍，但在「亞洲足球先生」擊敗中國球員武磊當選。<br />\n<br />\n轉自明報新聞網<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161202/s00006/1480613666553\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161202%2Fs00006%2F1480613666553&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY5kBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=af12ba82\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161202%2Fs00006%2F1480613666553&h=8785f2bb\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161202/s00006/1480613666553</a>"},{"pid":"52333545a97a6c2306522f922d52cc78a95a7b29","tid":17621,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:53:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"507ce31b969ea4f54cc5e09b00c090ad35de0b69","tid":17621,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:53:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ec2763ba13d730c6fac09609a876b298324beb5","tid":17621,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cd40a8734cc88f29b9e38dbd96678073606cf56","tid":17621,"uid":31089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:55:34.000Z","msg":"其待有一日佢可以進化成為黑椒牛筋丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4ce2c7ef6b9a5690b6946b86037e54891608cdf","tid":17621,"uid":2974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:56:09.000Z","msg":"真係好想同佢汗sex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ebe2b0f5e29dbd41e583329d253bf674ab463b2","tid":17621,"uid":9170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:57:33.000Z","msg":"你話我掃興都要講<br />\n<br />\n好丈部分仰吹捧出黎"},{"pid":"b33702bee45caff43ea7400f6a81abfb00cdbf39","tid":17621,"uid":9170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T01:58:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你話我掃興都要講<br />\n<br />\n好<del>丈</del>部分<del>仰</del>吹捧出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好大部分係吹捧出黎"},{"pid":"1f54d129fc2610cbb73ba16b0a70a4f919d857e9","tid":17621,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T02:01:16.000Z","msg":"點解武磊會有機會當選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df1531fd96f0e6b0fc81ff7450a78da78fe1647a","tid":17621,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T03:03:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}